3.000Z","msg":"鞋就Nike, Adidas, Vans, 平過香港好多，但款唔多<br />\n<br />\n女人袋淨係識Anges B, Longchamp 等相對比較平價的牌子。當香港（非水貨店）賣緊千幾蚊的袋，裏面可能賣緊五六百幾蚊。<br />\n<br />\n仲有個港女煲（Le Creuset，簡稱LC)在日本outlet買都平，可以買來轉手賣返比港女（尤其係限定版）。缺點係又重又易爛。裏面陶瓷狗兜都賣緊港紙二百幾蚊。<br />\n<br />\nQuicksilver有時有促銷，d背囊賣低過$100<br />\n<br />\n建議你去之前上outlet官網看下個floor plan先。<br />\n<br />\n另外outlet裏面唔係間間有退稅。你先上官網望下旅客有無咩優惠。有時要先去information center用護照換優惠券。"},{"pid":"7a1d931d119cd8d66380c3d8fea9855957fb3898","tid":101082,"uid":10666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T20:06:33.000Z","msg":"成班介紹d香港都有嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  united arrow , urban research , beams ,你可以當係貴小小嘅collect point，但係日本好出名，服飾上會比較斯文，cutting好適合香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a9d6d76e454e7e7c2e8031531115112984cffe","tid":101082,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T20:08:09.000Z","msg":"一定係beams <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n質地勁好又唔貴"},{"pid":"66b92ca20b1e8d474cb2c61cf24e041fedb19eb0","tid":101082,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定係beams <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n質地勁好又唔貴</blockquote><br />\n都唔會有咩好野會番係outlet啦"},{"pid":"889ddf06729683e9f74efc4999e85857f7097907","tid":101082,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:11:03.000Z","msg":"買左係咪唔著得<br />\n要等過關退稅?thx"},{"pid":"035696e41ba87368211690e78b295a5b307556e9","tid":101082,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買左係咪唔著得<br />\